constructive criticism, etc. If you feel you have been omitted from this
list in error, then please get in touch so it can be fixed. 

Contact
-------

If you find any bugs or problems in DeskLib, or if you can supply
suggestions or code for alterations, additions, or tutorial
applications, then please either write to Peter Naulls
(peter@chocky.org), who is the current DeskLib moderator, or raise it on
the DeskLib mailing list.